## Scarlett X Brain Protection

Each Scarlett persona has own encrypted brain for user content.

### Persona Brains

1. **Rose Brain**: Romantic, intimate content

1. **Eclipse Brain**: Dark, mysterious content

1. **Rain Brain**: Melancholic, emotional content

1. **Noir Brain**: Sophisticated, elegant content

### Protection Rules

1. **Persona Isolation**: Each persona can ONLY access own brain

1. **User Isolation**: Users can ONLY access own content

1. **Subscription Required**: Access requires active subscription

1. **Token Required**: All access requires persona-specific token

1. **Audit Logged**: All access logged

### Scarlett Access Example

```typescript
// Scarlett Rose requests token
const token = await oBrainAccessControl.requestToken(
  'scarlett_rose',        // Agent ID (must match persona)
  'scarlett_rose_brain',  // Brain ID (must match persona)
  'read',                 // Operation
  'scarlett_rose'         // Requested by
);

// Scarlett Rose accesses user content
const content = await scarlettXBrainAccess.accessContent(
  'rose',    // Persona
  userId,    // User ID
  token      // Token
);

// Returns ONLY content for this user and this persona
// Scarlett Rose CANNOT access Eclipse/Rain/Noir content
// Scarlett Rose CANNOT access other users' content
```

