## Emergency Procedures

### Agent Compromised

```typescript
// Mark agent as compromised
await oBrainAgentMonitor.markCompromised('haley', 'Suspicious behavior detected');

// This automatically:
// 1. Sets agent status to 'compromised'
// 2. Revokes all active tokens for agent
// 3. Blocks new token requests
// 4. Logs incident
```

### Token Revocation

```typescript
// Revoke specific token
await oBrainAccessControl.revokeToken(tokenId);

// Revoke all tokens for agent
await oBrainAccessControl.revokeAllAgentTokens('haley');
```

### Emergency Content Removal

```typescript
// Owner removes content (legal/safety)
await scarlettXBrainAccess.emergencyRemoveContent(
  contentId,
  ownerId,
  'Legal compliance - DMCA takedown'
);
```

### Kill Switch

```typescript
// Owner activates kill switch
// Shuts down all AI agents immediately
// Revokes all tokens
// Logs emergency shutdown
```

