## Performance Considerations

### Token Overhead

- Token request: ~50ms

- Token verification: ~10ms

- Total overhead: ~60ms per brain access

- Acceptable for most operations

- Cache tokens for repeated access

### Compression Savings

- 60-70% message size reduction

- Faster network transmission

- Lower bandwidth costs

- Reduced storage requirements

- Faster AI processing

### Database Load

- O-Brain adds ~5 tables

- Token storage: ~1KB per token

- Audit log: ~500 bytes per entry

- Estimated growth: ~1GB/year

- Regular cleanup of expired tokens

